        href=&quot;https://www.hellomagazine.com/tags/blake-lively/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Blake Lively&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was proposed to by Ryan Reynolds in 2012 with a rose gold engagement ring estimated to be worth around two million dollars. The
        slim pav&amp;eacute; band carries a huge 12-carat pink oval-cut diamond making for a rare combination.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Blake-Lively-Ring&quot;
