        jewels, but it was her off-duty look that tends to inspire us the most.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Prince Charles&amp;#39; former wife always looked stunning, whether she was dressed down on the way to the gym (hello cycling shorts and baggy sweaters) or
        popping to the shops carrying her &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hellomagazine.com/fashion/royal-style/20210707116978/princess-diana-gucci-bag-reformed-neon-straps/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gucci bag&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. She rocked many trends that
